{"ja388:0.1":"Jataka ","ja388:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","ja388:0.3":"Kharaputtavagga ","ja388:0.4":"3. Tundilajataka ","ja388:1.1":"“Navachannake dani diyyati, ","ja388:1.2":"Punnayam doni suvamini thita; ","ja388:1.3":"Bahuke jane pasapanike, ","ja388:1.4":"No ca kho me patibhati bhunjitum”. ","ja388:2.1":"“Tasasi bhamasi lenamicchasi, ","ja388:2.2":"Attanosi kuhim gamissasi; ","ja388:2.3":"Appossukko bhunja tundila, ","ja388:2.4":"Mamsatthaya hi positamhase. ","ja388:3.1":"Ogaha rahadam akaddamam, ","ja388:3.2":"Sabbam sedamalam pavahaya; ","ja388:3.3":"Ganhahi navam vilepanam, ","ja388:3.4":"Yassa gandho na kadaci chijjati”. ","ja388:4.1":"“Katamo rahado akaddamo, ","ja388:4.2":"Kimsu sedamalanti vuccati; ","ja388:4.3":"Katamanca navam vilepanam, ","ja388:4.4":"Yassa gandho na kadaci chijjati”. ","ja388:5.1":"“Dhammo rahado akaddamo, ","ja388:5.2":"Papam sedamalanti vuccati; ","ja388:5.3":"Silanca navam vilepanam, ","ja388:5.4":"Tassa gandho na kadaci chijjati. ","ja388:6.1":"Nandanti sariraghatino, ","ja388:6.2":"Na ca nandanti sariradharino; ","ja388:6.3":"Punnaya ca punnamasiya, ","ja388:6.4":"Ramamanava jahanti jivitan”ti. ","ja388:7.1":"Tundilajatakam tatiyam. "}